data.description: Welcome to 1270 Spruce Street! This lovely ranch style home is located in the desirable Blue Ridge Court neighborhood and the Falling Branch Elementary district in the heart of Christiansburg! You're close to everything you need & just minutes from both I81 and 460 for easy connectivity Blacksburg, Radford, and even Roanoke!  The classic floorplan offers one level living and an open kitchen and dining area for a seamless flow! The dining area opens up onto the covered back porch and fenced yard for easy indoor/outdoor entertaining! The attached carport has enough room for two cars and more!  With so much to offer, in addition to updates throughout, this is a great home to put your personal stamp on!
